text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 25.7.3, Group Exemption Procedures, Exempt Organization/Business Master File Handbook (EO/BMF).

The material relating to Group Exemption Procedures/Business Master File Handbook EO/BMF Exempt Organizations Extracts and On-Line Programs previously contained in IRM section 25.7.3 is incorporated into IRM 25.7.1 starting at IRM 25.7.1.7, continuing through IRM 25.7.1.12.
This supersedes and obsoletes IRM 25.7.3, Group Exemption Procedures/Business Master File Handbook EO/BMF Exempt Organizations Extracts and On-Line Programs, dated January 1, 2020.
Jennifer A. Jett Director, Business Systems Planning Shared Services Tax Exempt and Government Entities
